    "When the exponents are monomials of the same degree, their relative dominance order can be nicely visualised in the Stokes diagram of the connection (see Figure 2), which is obtained by plotting |e q | = e Re(q) as a function of d ∈ ∂ (for |z| ≫ 1) for each active circle ⟨q⟩.",
